name: CowTranslator
0:
”Alexa, ask cow translator what does the cow say?”
”Alexa, ask cow translator moo moo.”
”What does the cow say?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cow translator
des:
The skill will take a few short phrases and return the response in cow! The phrase could be simple, like "Moo moo," or 'What does the cow say?" 

Disclaimer: Results my vary. All cows may not understand each phrase.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
